item.title: About
item.description: Hey, My name is Nadeem Hilal, i am an Software Engineer by chance from a remote area of the world known as KASHMIR. I have completed my masters in Computer Applications aka (M.C.A) from the University of Kashmir North Campus. Currently i am living in DUBAI and alhamduliallah earing some bucks by working as a Software engineer. I have got in love with the CS (Software Engineering field) as i keep exploring it.
